I'll marry him,

293
00:15:22,790 --> 00:15:24,480
and he'll control Yuanfei Group's assets.

294
00:15:24,720 --> 00:15:25,600
Ambitious!

295
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:26,720
Here,

296
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:28,240
let me give you some tips.

297
00:15:28,840 --> 00:15:31,150
First, find the key to solving the problem.

298
00:15:31,550 --> 00:15:32,870
Between you and Xu Nuo,

299
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:34,120
there's Bai Xia standing in the way.

300
00:15:34,480 --> 00:15:35,360
You've never explained the misunderstanding

301
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:36,600
from back then, have you?

302
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:39,720
He won't explain,

303
00:15:40,240 --> 00:15:41,240
and I wouldn't believe him anyway.

304
00:15:41,790 --> 00:15:42,550
Next,

305
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:43,600
he'll launch

306
00:15:43,630 --> 00:15:45,200
an intense pursuit.

307
00:15:45,670 --> 00:15:47,750
Play hard to get,

308
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:49,440
keep her hanging,

309
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:52,200
then take control.

310
00:15:53,510 --> 00:15:54,910
No matter his tricks,

311
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:56,270
we won't lose out.

312
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:58,840
If you don't fall for him,

313
00:15:59,150 --> 00:16:00,320
he'll have to hand over

314
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:01,630
his CEO position at Yuanfei Group.

315
00:16:02,480 --> 00:16:03,600
Even if you do fall for him,

316
00:16:03,870 --> 00:16:05,080
don't admit it easily.

317
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:06,670
After all, you're the one who decides.

318
00:16:07,120 --> 00:16:07,670
No,

319
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:11,870
I won't fall for him.

320
00:16:12,150 --> 00:16:13,790
It's impossible.

