00:16:22,220 --> 00:16:25,060
[CEO's Office]

322
00:16:25,910 --> 00:16:27,240
"Last night, Mr. Shen and his assistant's

323
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:29,030
passionate moment against the office glass door

324
00:16:29,390 --> 00:16:30,840
was 'thoughtfully' recorded by security cameras.

325
00:16:31,550 --> 00:16:33,240
Poor glass doors!"

326
00:16:34,550 --> 00:16:35,630
"It's just a stepping stone

327
00:16:35,630 --> 00:16:36,960
in Mr. Shen's love chase."

328
00:16:40,150 --> 00:16:41,840
That's so embarrassing.

329
00:16:49,480 --> 00:16:50,720
Looks like Yuanfei Group's stock rose again.

330
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:51,910
It's now...

331
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:53,270
18.7 yuan per share.

332
00:16:57,200 --> 00:16:58,390
As Mr. Shen's assistant,

333
00:16:58,630 --> 00:16:59,360
if I don't

334
00:16:59,360 --> 00:17:00,150
immediately understand

335
00:17:00,150 --> 00:17:01,030
such simple things,

336
00:17:01,440 --> 00:17:02,630
isn't that negligence?

337
00:17:03,630 --> 00:17:04,400
Right, Mr. Shen?

338
00:17:04,640 --> 00:17:06,350
Nicely done, Assistant Xu.

339
00:17:10,900 --> 00:17:12,020
[Bai Xia]

340
00:17:13,160 --> 00:17:13,510
Hello?

341
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:16,200
Jiahe...

342
00:17:18,160 --> 00:17:19,640
my mom came to see me again yesterday.

343
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:21,510
I couldn't sleep all night.

344
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:23,070
After thinking it over,

345
00:17:23,400 --> 00:17:24,680
I decided to call you.

346
00:17:24,750 --> 00:17:25,640
Get to the point.

347
00:17:26,510 --> 00:17:28,030
She's asking for 300,000.

348
00:17:28,750 --> 00:17:29,880
How does that concern me?

349
00:17:30,790 --> 00:17:31,750
She threatened

350
00:17:32,440 --> 00:17:33,110
if I don't pay,

351
00:17:33,920 --> 00:17:34,750
she'll expose my fake education

352
00:17:34,750 --> 00:17:35,550
and fake family background,

353
00:17:35,550 --> 00:17:37,480
everything...

354
00:17:38,110 --> 00:17:38,640
Got it.

355
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:39,790
Ao Zhe will handle it.

356
00:17:40,070 --> 00:17:40,550
I'm hanging up.

357
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:43,070
Shen Jiahe,

358
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:45,030
you really know how to fool around.

359
00:17:45,200 --> 00:17:46,720
You're completely shameless.

360
00:17:46,880 --> 00:17:48,550
Compared to your ex-boyfriends,

361
00:17:48,790 --> 00:17:49,920
I still have a long way to go.

362
00:17:51,510 --> 00:17:52,480
True.

363
00:17:53,960 --> 00:17:56,000
Being a jerk requires some talent,

364
00:17:56,590 --> 00:17:58,310
and you're not quite there yet.

365
00:18:03,550 --> 00:18:05,550
Want to play this love game, huh?

366
00:18:06,590 --> 00:18:08,680
I'll make sure you lose completely.

367
00:18:17,530 --> 00:18:23,030
♪I love you, love you, love you♪

